# Third-party notices

## A1 delegation evidence design (MIT)

The delegation-evidence verify layer in `src/integrations/a1-evidence/` adapts the
cryptographic delegation certificate and chain design from the **A1** project:

- **Project:** https://github.com/dyologician/A1
- **License:** MIT (see upstream `LICENSE`)

Handshake re-namespaces Ed25519/BLAKE3 domain separators to `handshake::delegation::*::v1`,
ships an independent TypeScript verifier (`handshake-delegation-1.0.0-zip215`), and does
**not** intend wire interoperability with live A1 `a1::dyolo::` chains. Attribution is
required; upstream code is not vendored in this repository.
